{"tid":1243701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賤婦毒計] 林賤扮死狗，係因為想在G20瘋會前結束示威","createTime":"2019-06-19T14:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T05:30:23.000Z","uid":217761,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"55b70751239827ca57856eacd880c984e7cefbca","tid":1243701,"uid":217761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"習豬頭將會於六月底出席G20瘋會，如果示威未平息， 到時好可能會被侵侵為首的多個國家圍攻；相反，如果6月底前林賤將示威平息，習豬頭就可以在G20瘋會同全世界講香港的示威已經和平結束，而歐美等國亦無能為力，等到G20瘋會完結，林賤妖婦就會重推惡法，並清算所以示威者，<br />\n所以，信我，不要中共狗緩兵之計，示威行動一定要堅持到六月底，並將問題繼續發酵，帶上 G20 瘋會，逼習豬頭讓步，否則往後打壓將會非常激烈"},{"pid":"8d8e75ea6c77d4c7f35b5ce00672ed66030d599f","tid":1243701,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期五"},{"pid":"2698eadb0fd681fa13419e57a349a4e91d4cb2c3","tid":1243701,"uid":217761,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8d8e75ea6c77d4c7f35b5ce00672ed66030d599f","tid":1243701,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期五"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"呢件賤婦好撚陰毒，暫緩就係為左G20之後重推惡法，<br />\n佢係絕對絕對唔會罷休，<br />\n離月底時間唔係好多，一定要將件事繼續推撚爆佢，推到去 G20，<br />\n否則往後打壓會更嚴重"},{"pid":"0324163441a41f49998fc5c5ddd4ca0814e521b5","tid":1243701,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:55:23.000